NOTICE IS HERBY GIVEN: Red Rock Financial Services, officially assigned as agent by the Cottage
Grove Estates Homeowners Association, Inc, which the Lien for Delinquent Assessments was executed and
affecting the following described property situated in the County of Nye, State of Nevada, and more commonly
known as:
210 S Magnolia Blvd, Pahrump, NV 89048
COTTAGE GROVE ESTATES LOT 11 BLOCK 3, recorded at the Nye County, Nevada Recorders
Office.
The owner(s) of record on said Lien: GLENN A BAKER AND KATHLEEN M BAKER
The Lien for Delinquent Assessments recorded at the Nye County, Nevada Recorders Office on 01/06/2022 as
Book Number , as Instrument Number 973554, against above said property is hereby released and satisfied.

Homeowners Association, Inc
STATE OF NEVADA

the instrument the person, or the entity upon behalf of which the person acted, executed the instrument.
